svg.text: Starting ScreenThe user click on the Get Startedto sign up or sign in
Searh (Home) ScreenThe user can select "Source type","Citation style," and "Search input"to narrow down the search results,then click on the arrow button.
Library ScreenAt the library, the user can reviewall citations had saved before andcreate a new folder as well.
A Selected FolderWhen the user is at the folder screen,they can share the folder with friendsand view the citation as well as theentire paper by clicking on it.
Profile ScreenAt the sidebar menu, the user canconnect with their friends to sharecitations when working together onany project.

A Selected PaperAfter selecting the search result,the user can now view the citationpart as well as the entire paper. Inorder to store a citation, click on the"Store" button. The user can specificallyhighlight any sentence on the paper.
A Pop-up FolderA pop-up card will appearafter that. The user needs to namethe folder and title name, thenclicking on the "Create" button.
Search ResultsIt will show the results based onthe keywords.
Sign Up ScreenThere are three ways for the user tosign up. Once a user has signedupbefore, they can click on "Alreadyhave an account".
Sign In ScreenThere are three ways for the user tosign in. The user can create an accountby clicking on "Do not have an account?",if this is their first time using the app.
